mistral.reason: "Zhejiangosaurus" was incorrectly identified as "Zhejiangosaurus luoyangensis" in the study by Lü et al., 2007, but it has been updated to "Zhejiangosaurus lishuiensis" in recent studies (Leahey et al., 2015). Therefore, there is no parent-authority relationship between Zhejiangosaurus and the study by Lü et al., 2007.
